In your jest.config.ts, set up separate projects for unit and integration tests:

```typescript
export default {
  projects: [
    {
      displayName: 'unit',
      testMatch: ['<rootDir>/tests/unit/**/*.test.ts'],
      transform: { '^.+\\.ts$': 'ts-jest' }
    },
    {
      displayName: 'integration',
